Tailwind CSS sidebar

Utilize the sidebar feature to display a roster of menu items and multi-tiered menu selections flanking both sides of the page, facilitating navigation throughout your website.

The sidebar module serves as a supplementary constituent aligned with the navbar, appearing on either the left or right side of the page for navigation within your web application. It encompasses an array of elements, comprising menu items, multi-tiered menu options, call-to-action elements, and beyond.
